name: Corsia Logistics
overview:
Corsia LLC is licensed and insured with USDOT and FMCSA full service auto transport company.

The company transports all makes and models of vehicles - from standard SUVs and sedans to exotic, sports and classic vehicles. Customers can request either enclosed or open auto transport.

Corsia’s website offers easy to use car shipping quote form. Corsia Logistics hires only verified carriers with high safety ratings and solid experience to provide customers with efficient and affordable service. A team of car relocation specialists and professional dispatchers is always on standby ready to help.
